    "body": "Closes #38940\r\n\r\n## Problem:\r\nMany users want :restart to restore their session and window/tabpage layout.\r\n\r\n## Solution:\r\nAdd :restart! which saves the session before restarting (using v:this_session if set, otherwise stdpath('state')/restart_session.vim), then sources it on the new server. Session save failure aborts the restart with E5807. Unsaved buffers prompt via :confirm.  \r\nThis is meant to be the \"inital best effort\" mentioned in the issue.\r\n\r\nAI-assisted: OpenCode",
